description	"Imperial 501st Swamptrooper

^2Weapons:
- SE-14R Repeating Blaster (2)
- Modified E-11 Blaster Rifle (2)
-- Based on Clone Rifle
- 2 Frag Grenades

^8Attributes:
- 1 Reinforcement
- Assemble (1)

501st stormtroopers were the Elite Clonetroopers who became Vader's Fist following operation nightfall. Having witnessed many of their fellows killed by the rebels following the destruction of the Deathstar, these few but Elite men are eager to exact revenge. "